20deff4a67b36734dbdd639d6147e3b8a737c593.title: BABYMONSTER - ‘FOREVER’ M/V REACTION
20deff4a67b36734dbdd639d6147e3b8a737c593.description:
When you ask for a blend of retro/disco/hip hop, I guess this is what you get! And so that was a really nice surprise, quite unexpected I have to admit! That said, it is definitely not the first time that YG dabbles in retro sounds, but still I don't think I was imaging BAEMON to tackle such genre so quickly. They killed the raps, once again! Hate it or not, their rappers are gold! The vocals, as always, magical and I love the ad libs here! This got me thinking of a world cup song almost, but I think it's because of the more disco/retro approach of the song. I would say this is more of a grower than an instant hit for me though. The MV, I wished they pushed the whole 'Cinderella' concept a bit further because I'm a sucker for fairy tale retelling!  But other than that, it was a really nice and enjoyable comeback, one that I think could potentially please a broader audience than their past two title tracks.

3882ff24fdb79a7304252441acd8441b16156b6a.description:
The Supreme Court issues a landmark ruling saying former President Trump has immunity for official presidential acts. The Biden campaign continues to push back against suggestions that the president should step aside after a poor debate performance. Trump ally Steve Bannon begins his four-month prison sentence for defying a congressional subpoena. France’s far-right wins big in the first round of parliamentary elections.

29:11 Biden campaign ad addresses age concerns post-debate
40:10 Steve Bannon reports to prison to begin 4-month prison term
46:05 Far-right wins first round of parliamentary elections in France
